---
title:  Cheese and Chickpea Gyros with sweet chilli yoghurt filling
description: The name of this Greek dish literally translates as 'turn' because of the rotisserie cooking method it usually employs. Though Gyros are traditionally made with meat, this veggie version filled with chickpeas and cheese is just as delicious as the original.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/HF_Y23_R08_W06_IE_EQVV13087-2_Main_high-93ad1a27.jpg
